  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_21",
    "text": "Currently in its second season, the six-team league is already looking to the future and could expand as soon as the 2o25-26 campaign.",
