  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_9",
    "text": "Now it will be the setting for an- other first as her league-leading Victoire (3-2-1-1) and the Sceptes (2-0-1-4) battle in the first Cana- dian stop of the PWHL's \"Take- over Tour.\"",
