  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_16",
    "text": "Fans in both Victoire and Sceptres jerseys milled around thegates at Rogers Arena on Tues- day afternoon, hoping to catch a glimpse of their favourite players. The fact that people living thousands of kilometres away from Montreal own Victoire gear shows the PWHL is a movement, Poulin said.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
