    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_19",
    "text": "\"Honestly, seeing kids wearing different jerseys with our names on with different logos, for us, that's what it's all about,\"she said. \"We want to grow the league. We're doing this by playing our best. we're just putting our best product on the ice, and it's been amazing to see.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
