  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_36",
    "text": "Beyond that is the perhaps the biggest question for golf fans: Even if the PGA Tour strikes a deal with PIF, what does that mean for the great divide in golf? what be- comes of LIv?",
