  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_37",
    "text": "\"soon there should be more move- ment,\" Scott said. \"But it's very difficult to bring all of this together, certainly from a competitions layout. It's a lot. Someone has to compromise their product. I don't like the sound of that generally. Who's go- ing to do it? Everyone a little bit? That's not good. Someone alot? That person is not go- ing to be happy.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7408333333333333,
      0.8027860696517413,
      0.9666666666666667,
      0.8616915422885573
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_28",
    "text": "The new PGA Tour Enterprises received US$1.s-billion in funding from Strategic Sports Group and created a plan for players to receive equity shares. The first big change in eligibility in more than 40 years led to only 1oo players from the FedEx Cup keeping cards this year, and fi eld sizes will shrink in 2026.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0325,
      0.8354228855721393,
      0.25916666666666666,
      0.8875621890547264
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_38",
    "text": "\"It's really a tricky one.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7533333333333333,
      0.8616915422885573,
      0.8816666666666667,
      0.8680597014925373
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_39",
    "text": "LIV starts its fourth season next month in Saudi Arabia. It filled out its 14-tourna- ment schedule on Tuesday by adding stops at Trump Doral near Miami, the Robert Trent Jones Golf Club in Virginia, Chapulte- pec in Mexico City and a course in Michi- gan that opened only last year.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.74,
      0.8676616915422886,
      0.9658333333333333,
      0.914228855721393
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_29",
    "text": "All the while, the affable Australian is part of the PGA Tour Enterprises transac- tion subcommittee with Tiger Woods and Rory McIlroy that is negotiating with the Saudi backers of LIV Golf to become a mi- nority investor.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0325,
      0.8879601990049751,
      0.25833333333333336,
      0.9265671641791045
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_40",
    "text": "Sports Business Journal and most re- cently The Daily Telegraph have reported on advanced negotiations for LIv to get a TV deal with Fox, although the network might need more than 14 tournaments to make it worthwhile. IMG owns the interna- tional media rights to the Asian Tour, in which LIV has invested heavily, creating the International Series. Bryson DeCham- beau will be among those playing in India later this month.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7408333333333333,
      0.9138308457711443,
      0.9666666666666667,
      0.9866666666666667
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_30",
    "text": "And how's that going?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04583333333333333,
      0.9273631840796019,
      0.16666666666666666,
      0.9333333333333333
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_31",
    "text": "\"same as always. Itsucks,\"Scott said in a hallway below the clubhouse at Kapalua, more matter-of-fact than showing any lev- el of irritation. \"It's not worth talking about. Obviously, it's so complex and when the government department is involved, I think we sit and just wait for them.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.03333333333333333,
      0.9337313432835821,
      0.25833333333333336,
      0.9791044776119403
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 37
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_18",
    "text": "Adam Scott says there should soon be some progress on how, or if, the PGA Tour will itegrate its competitions with the Saudi-backed LIV Golf. MATT YORK/THE ASSOCIATED PRE:",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2791666666666667,
      0.9400995024875622,
      0.7183333333333334,
      0.9532338308457712
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 38
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_35",
    "text": "",
