  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027_34",
    "text": "By all accounts, the PGA Tour and the Public Investment Fund are closer than ev- er to an agreement and it would not be sur- prising if a deal was announced by The Players Championship in March. But much depends on the U.S. Justice Department, with which the tour has been in touch ev- ery step of the way in negotiations. Further muddling the issue is a change in power at the white House in two weeks.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.27,
      0.96,
      0.49416666666666664,
      0.992636815920398
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Globe and Mail - 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_027",
    "order": 40
  },
  {
